description:
PowerDistribution: Table recording power distribution status for a cell site, including timestamps, location, cell ID, alarm thresholds, and availability.
- dateTime: Timestamp of the power distribution status record.
- Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell site.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant cell site identifier (appears to be the same as CellId).
- Id3:  Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear from single sample).
- vsDataType: Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion:  Version of the data format.
- PowerDistribution.userLabel: User-defined label (currently empty).
- PowerDistribution.systemUndervoltageAlarmLevel: System undervoltage alarm threshold (in mV).
- PowerDistribution.systemOvervoltageAlarmLevel: System overvoltage alarm threshold (in mV).
- PowerDistribution.availabilityStatus: Current availability status of the power distribution system.
- PowerDistribution.powerDistributionId: Unique identifier for the power distribution system.
